    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You stomp the ground with incredible force causing a boulder to be chinked from the ground in front of you. You then make a frontflip, channeling earth release chakra to increase your strength, grab the boulder and throw it at a creature within range.</p><p>Make a ranged taijutsu attack, dealing your unarmed damage + 3d6 Earth damage and the creature must make a Constitution saving throw, becoming Dazed on a failure.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost by 3, the damage by 2d6, and the range by 15ft.</p>",
